# MRI Segmentations

This directory contains manual claustrum segmentations from three in vivo 7-Tesla MP2RAGE MRI
datasets acquired at isotropic resolutions of 0.5 mm, 0.7 mm, and 1.0 mm (n=10 per dataset).
Segmentations were performed manually by author SP in each subject's native space. 

---

## Label system

| Label | Structure |
| --- | --- |
| `1` | Left claustrum |
| `2` | Right claustrum |

---

## Datasets

| Dataset | Resolution | N | Source |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 0p5 | 0.5 mm isotropic | 10 | [Cabalo et al. (2025)](https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-025-04863-7) |
| 0p7 | 0.7 mm isotropic | 10 | [Haast et al. (2024)](https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.2310044121) |
| 1p0 | 1.0 mm isotropic | 10 | [Kashyap et al. (2018)](https://doi.org/10.1016/j.neuroimage.2017.07.022) |

Full acquisition details are provided in Table 1 of the accompanying manuscript.
